GDIS Debian packaging notes
===========================

This packaging refresh intentionally builds the renewed GTK4/OpenGL path and
does not use the legacy GTK2 + gtkglext stack that remains in the upstream
tree for historical compatibility.

The packaged executable is installed as:

  /usr/lib/gdis/gdis

Runtime data files expected by GDIS live beside that binary:

  /usr/lib/gdis/gdis.elements
  /usr/lib/gdis/gdis.library
  /usr/lib/gdis/gdis.manual

A small wrapper is installed as:

  /usr/bin/gdis

That wrapper preserves the current runtime lookup behavior without needing a
larger upstream path-handling refactor during the initial Debian refresh.
